  * Fix version display: bump frontend/package.json to 0.1.6 so postinst
    rebuild bakes the correct version string into the Next.js static build.
    Previous 0.1.5 deploy left frontend title showing v0.1.4 because apt
    skipped reinstall of an already-installed 0.1.5 package.

