    packages.tsx that caused Turbopack "Return statement is not allowed here"
    errors, breaking the frontend build entirely.
  * Fix postinst: clean node_modules and .next before rebuilding to avoid
    stale cache issues; force NODE_ENV=development so devDependencies
    (tailwindcss, typescript, etc.) are installed during package setup.

